data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLERS! Your own private oasis close to amenities. Come home to this beautifully kept, 4bed/2bath home sitting on almost half an acre in a peaceful neighborhood. Much love and attention has been given to this property with attractive improvements made both outside and in every room inside. With new appliances, windows, flooring, and major upgrades to each bathroom, this home is more than ready for you! Home has successfully operated as a VRBO and provides huge income potential. Railroad tracks in back of property are active - used only by Weyerhaeuser once per day. Vinyl fence in driveway is set up for easy removal.  Make it yours! Call Crystal Purvis at 406-249-9070 or your real estate professional today!
